Add ``docs/llm-integration.md`` documenting boo-cloud quirks an LLM (or LLM-driven workflow) is most likely to be confused by — notably that ``start_print`` returns ``result: "sent"`` with ``return_code: -1`` and ``print_result: -999`` as the **success** path, not an error. Also expand the ``start_print`` MCP docstring with the same explanation so it surfaces in the tool description.
